{"data":{"page":{"id":"afe1abd0-a714-5290-ba95-fff2fa0101db","html":"<p>As part of WCRS pitching activities, I was asked to build an iPad prototype with one user journey showcasing the product catalog and product selection based on style, mood and colour.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/667385ebdd1a6f9a1c8421badb2b9aca/40247/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.7%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/667385ebdd1a6f9a1c8421badb2b9aca/6b333/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/667385ebdd1a6f9a1c8421badb2b9aca/f3ce7/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/667385ebdd1a6f9a1c8421badb2b9aca/72342/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/667385ebdd1a6f9a1c8421badb2b9aca/6b333/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/667385ebdd1a6f9a1c8421badb2b9aca/40247/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<video class=\"full-img\" style=\"border: 1px solid #CCC; border-radius: 30px;\" width=\"100%\" controls>\n    <source src=\"/bandq-83e5c79ee6a870953d24fa106391ab5e.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n</video>","fields":{"prefix":"2013-01-06"},"frontmatter":{"title":"B&Q prototype","cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/bandq/","source":"work"}}